        "timestamp": "2018-02-06 01:11:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nLiang, good patch, curious as to how logs are showing in the elk stack (onap-log) and the use cases to emit logs\n\nto enable the logs see\n\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=24642176",
        "patchset_number": 2
