      {
        "id": "7c9713ee0ed7f65933961545a1de262729d70b37",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 129,
          "name": "Luke Parker",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "lparker@amdocs.com",
          "username": "lparker"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-02-06 03:51:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nVery nice, and I'm looking forward to seeing the final paths. Echoing Michael's feedback, I'm interested to see how close you've managed to get to the output expected by Filebeat + Logstash, described at https://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=20087036#ONAPApplicationLoggingGuidelinesv1.2(Beijing)-OutputFormat. Other output formats can be supported relatively easily in the near-term, but at the cost of maintaining special cases (in those configurations) in the longer term. We'll eagerly assist with fine-tuning the output, if that's helpful.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "1098cd5477bd0cf29f400206ba4d3e4d3f4a60a2",
