        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-02-06 08:12:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nMichael and Luke, I got your points. Currently I have been developing python log project. for my opinion, I should apply this project in MultiCloud  that help us to flexibly define the output format, handlers and filters in log configuration , then I will submit a new patch include  expected output format in log configuration.",
        "patchset_number": 2
