        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nHi Borislav Glozman, Because vio and framework service do not log swagger api request information, you could call other apis to log information. \nFor VIO example:\ncurl -X GET  http://<ip:9004>/api/multicloud-vio/v0/vmware_vio/identity/v3\nFor framework example:\ncurl -X GET  http://<ip:9001>/api/multicloud/v0/vmware_vio/identity/v3\n\nMore multicloud api can refer to: http://onap.readthedocs.io/en/latest/submodules/multicloud/framework.git/docs",
        "patchset_number": 6
      },
